IRKeyboardEmu: 	Apple IR Remote Emulation
What:		The title pretty much says it all.
Why:		To simulate the effects of an Apple Remote on Mac OS X
Who:		Brandon Holland (bholland@brandon-holland.com)
		Evan Schoenberg (@evands)
Where:		http://brandon-holland.com/software/irkeyboardemu
Version:	0.5

Install:
sudo chown -R root:wheel IRKeyboardEmu.kext
sudo chmod -R 755 IRKeyboardEmu.kext
sudo kextload IRKeyboardEmu.kext

Usage:
sudo sysctl -w kern.sendIR=[0 - 17]

